com.vector.cfg.util.scripting.dynamic

Annotation Type DynamicTarget


  • @Documented
 @Retention(value=CLASS)
 @Target(value=TYPE)
 @PublishedApi(value=CLASS_DEPENDENCY)
 @PublishedApiDomain(value=AUTOMATION_IF)
public @interface DynamicTarget
    DynamicTarget marks the types that it is enriched at runtime which the specified type. This annotation helps IDEs to provide code completion at compile time for runtime enhanced types.
